    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BlueButton, BlueFreeTile, BlueWallTile, BombTile, BrownButton, DirtTile, DoorTile, ExitTile, FireTile, ForceFloorDownTile, ForceFloorLeftTile, ForceFloorRightTile, ForceFloorTile, ForceFloorUpTile, FreeTile, GravelTile, GreenButton, HiddenWallTile, HintTile, IceTile, InvisibleWallTile, RecessedWallTile, RedButton, SocketTile, TeleportTile, TimerWallTile, ToggleWallTile, TrapTile, WallTile, WaterTile

    public abstract class Tile
extends GameObject
    Abstract super tile class, contains functions required by every tile irregardless of it's type. The class simple contains the listeners that will be run on each event process, the position of the tile, and the type of the tile.
